quran[57]{c,v,t}:
  73,20,"Mu by’ukuri, Nyagasani wawe azi ko wowe (Muhamadi) n’itsinda muri kumwe mubyuka mugasenga hafi bibiri bya gatatu by’ijoro, cyangwa icya kabiri cyaryo, cyangwa se icya gatatu cyaryo. Kandi Allah ni we ugena indeshyo y’ijoro n’amanywa. Azi ko mutari gushobora gusenga ijoro ryose, bityo yabagiriye impuhwe (araborohereza). Ku bw’ibyo, mujye musoma ibiboroheye muri Qur’an. Azi ko muri mwe hazabamo abarwayi, abandi bakaba bari mu ngendo bashakisha ingabire za Allah, naho abandi bakazaba bari ku rugamba barwana mu nzira ya Allah. Bityo, mujye musoma ibiboroheye muri yo, muhozeho amasengesho, mutange amaturo, munagurize Allah inguzanyo nziza (mutanga kubera we). Kandi icyiza cyose mwiteganyirije imbere, muzagisanga kwa Allah ari cyiza kurushaho kandi gifite ibihembo bihebuje. Munasabe imbabazi Allah, kuko mu by’ukuri Allah ari Nyirimpuhwe, Nyirimbabazi"
  74,1,Yewe uwitwikiriye (uvugwa aha ni Intumwa Muhamadi)
  74,2,Haguruka uburire (ibiremwa)
  74,3,Unahe ikuzo Nyagasani wawe
  74,4,Unasukure imyambaro yawe
  74,5,Unitarure ibigirwamana
  74,6,Ntukanatange (ikintu) ugamije indonke
  74,7,Kandi ujye wihangana kubera Nyagasani wawe
  74,8,Ubwo impanda izavuzwa
  74,9,Uwo munsi uzaba ari umunsi ukomeye
  74,10,Uzaba utoroheye abahakanyi
  74,11,(Yewe Muhamadi) ndekera uwo naremye ari wenyine (uvugwa aha ni Al Walid bun al Mughirat)
  74,12,Nkamuha imitungo itubutse
  74,13,N’urubyaro rumukikije
  74,14,Nkanamworohereza ubuzima
  74,15,"Nyuma y’ibyo byose, akaba yifuza ko namwongera"
  74,16,"Oya! Mu by’ukuri, yajyaga ahinyura amagambo yacu cyane"
  74,17,Nzamunaniza muhanisha ibihano bikomeye
  74,18,"Mu by’ukuri, yatekereje (ku byo avuga) maze afata umwanzuro (wo gutuka Allah n’Intumwa ye ndetse na Qur’an)"
  74,19,"Bityo, navumwe kubera umwanzuro yafashe"
  74,20,Niyongere avumwe kubera umwanzuro yafashe
  74,21,Nuko (yubura amaso) areba (abari bamukikije)
  74,22,"Maze azinga umunya, akambya agahanga"
  74,23,"Nuko atera umugongo (ukuri), maze aribona"
  74,24,"Aravuga ati \"Ibi (Muhamadi yigisha) nta kindi biri cyo uretse ko ari uburozi (akomora ku barozi bo hambere bakomeye)"
  74,25,Ibi (Muhamadi yigisha) nta kindi biri cyo uretse ko ari amagambo y’umuntu
  74,26,Nzamwinjiza mu muriro
  74,27,N’iki cyakumenyesha uwo muriro
  74,28,Ntacyo ureka ndetse nta n’icyo usigaza
  74,29,Utwika imibiri ukanayishiririza
  74,30,Urinzwe (n’abamalayika) cumi n’icyenda
  74,31,"Kandi nta bandi twagize abarinzi b’umuriro batari abamalayika. Ndetse twanashyizeho umubare wabo (cumi n’icyenda) kugira ngo tugerageze abahakanyi, no kugira ngo abahawe ibitabo bemere badashidikanya (ko Qur’an ari ukuri kuko ihuriye kuri uwo mubare wanditse mu bitabo byabo); ndetse no kugira ngo abemeramana barusheho kwemera, no kugira ngo abahawe igitabo n’abemeramana batagira ugushidikanya (ku byo bemeye), ndetse no kugira ngo abafite uburwayi (bw’uburyarya) mu mitima n’abahakanyi bavuge bati \" Allah yari agamije iki mu gutanga uru rugero?\" Uko ni ko Allah arekera mu buyobe uwo ashatse akanayobora uwo ashatse. Kandi nta wamenya ingabo za Nyagasani wawe utari we. Kandi uyu (muriro) nta kindi uri cyo usibye ko ari urwibutso ku bantu"
  74,32,Oya si ko biri! Ndahiriye ku kwezi
  74,33,No ku ijoro igihe ricyeye
  74,34,No ku gitondo igihe gitangaje
  74,35,"Mu by’ukuri, uwo (muriro) ni kimwe mu (byago) bihambaye"
  74,36,Ukaba n’umuburizi ku bantu
  74,37,K’uwo ari we wese muri mwe ushaka kujya imbere (yiyegereza Nyagasani we) cyangwa gusubira inyuma (amwigomekaho)
  74,38,Buri wese azafungirwa (mu muriro) bitewe n’ibibi yakoze
  74,39,Uretse abantu b’iburyo (b’abemera nyakuri)
  74,40,"Bazaba bari mu busitani (Ijuru), babazanya"
  74,41,"Ku byerekeye inkozi z’ibibi, (maze bazibaze bati)"
  74,42,Ni iki cyabateye kuba muri mu muriro
  74,43,"(Izo nkozi z’ibibi) zizavuga ziti \"Ntitwari bamwe mu basenga"
  74,44,Nta n’ubwo twajyaga tugaburira abakene
  74,45,Kandi twajyaga tugirana ibiganiro n’abavuga ibidafite umumaro
  74,46,Ndetse twajyaga duhinyura umunsi w’ibihembo (imperuka)
  74,47,Kugeza ubwo ukuri kudashidikanywaho (urupfu) kutugezeho
  74,48,"Bityo, nta buvugizi bw’abavugizi buzagira icyo bubamarira"
  74,49,Nonese ni iyihe mpamvu ituma (abahakanyi) batera umugongo urwibutso
  74,50,Bameze nk’imparage ziruka (zifite ubwoba)
  74,51,Zihunga intare
  74,52,Ahubwo buri wese muri bo aba ashaka ko yahishurirwa ibitabo birambuye (bishimangira ko Isilamu ari idini ry’ukuri)
  74,53,Oya si ko biri! Ahubwo ntibatinya umunsi w’imperuka
  74,54,"Oya si ko biri! Mu by’ukuri, iyi (Qur’an) ni urwibutso"
  74,55,"Bityo, ushaka (ko imubera urwibutso) nayibuke (ayisoma, anatekereza ku nyigisho ziyikubiyemo)"
  74,56,"Kandi ntibashobora kwibuka keretse Allah abishatse. Ni we ukwiriye gutinywa, ndetse ni na we utanga imbabazi"